title: Get Clear on Your Goals
itunes:title: Get Clear on Your Goals
description:
Episode 366 - One of the main issues I see with people and their goals is lack of clarity. The more clearly that you can see your target the better chance you have of hitting in. In this episode, I break down how to get very clear on what it is that you want.
